    />

    <style>
      /* â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
         1. FIXED HEADER CLEARANCE
         â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• */
      section.py-clearance {
        padding-top: 120px !important;
        padding-bottom: 80px !important;
      }

      /* â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
         2. BASE THEME
         â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• */
      html { overflow-x: hidden !important; }
      body {
        overflow-x: hidden !important;
        max-width: 100vw !important;
        background-color: #0a0e14 !important;
        color: #ffffff !important;
      }

      /* â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
         3. GRADIENT TEXT
         â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• */
      .gradient-text {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, #0fbc6d 60%, #22c55e 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
        font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 6vw, 3.5rem) !important;
        line-height: 1.2 !important;
        display: block;
      }

      /* â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
         4. SECTION DIVIDER
         â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• */
      .section-divider {
        border: 0;
        position: relative;
        margin: 3rem 0;
        height: 32px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }
      .section-divider::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        left: 0; right: 0; top: 50%;
        transform: translateY(-50%);
        height: 1px;
        background: linear-gradient(
          to right,
          transparent 0%,
          rgba(15,188,109,0.15) 8%,
          rgba(15,188,109,0.45) 30%,
          rgba(15,188,109,0.45) 70%,
          rgba(15,188,109,0.15) 92%,
          transparent 100%
        );
      }
      .section-divider::after {
        content: '';
        position: relative;
        width: 8px; height: 8px;
        background: #0fbc6d;
        border-radius: 2px;
        transform: rotate(45deg);
        box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(15,188,109,0.6);
        flex-shrink: 0;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      /* â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
         5. CARD GRID
         â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• */
      .cards-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 1.25rem;
      }
      @media (min-width: 640px)  { .cards-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
      @media (min-width: 1024px) { .cards-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); } }

      /* â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
         6. PROJECT CARD â€” GLASSMORPHISM
         â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• */
      .project-card {
        width: 100%;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04) !important;
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07) !important;
        border-radius: 1rem !important;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        overflow: hidden;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
      }
      .project-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-6px) scale(1.01);
        box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(15,188,109,0.15);
        border-color: rgba(15,188,109,0.3) !important;
      }
      .project-card.border-t-green  { border-top: 4px solid #22c55e !important; }
      .project-card.border-t-yellow { border-top: 4px solid #eab308 !important; }
      .project-card.border-t-cyan   { border-top: 4px solid #06b6d4 !important; }

      .project-card .card-img-wrap {
        position: relative;
        height: 180px;
        overflow: hidden;
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }
      .project-card .card-img-wrap img {
        width: 100%; height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        transition: transform 0.35s ease;
      }
      .project-card:hover .card-img-wrap img { transform: scale(1.08); }

      /* â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
         7. CARD CONTENT CONSISTENCY
         â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• */
      .card-title {
        min-height: 3.2rem;
        display: -webkit-box;
        -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
        -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .card-desc {
        min-height: 4.5rem;
        display: -webkit-box;
        -webkit-line-clamp: 3;
        -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      /* â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
         8. BADGE
         â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• */
      .card-badge {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0.5rem; left: 0.5rem;
        background: rgba(10,14,20,0.75);
        backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 0.65rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        padding: 0.2rem 0.65rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
      }

      /* â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
         9. SECTION HEADING
         â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• */
      .section-heading {
        font-size: 1.35rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #fff;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        padding-left: 1rem;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
      }
      .section-heading .heading-bar {
        display: inline-block;
        width: 4px; height: 1.4em;
        border-radius: 2px;
        margin-right: 0.75rem;
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }

      .loading-text {
        color: #6b7280;
        animation: pulse 2s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.6,1) infinite;
      }
      @keyframes pulse {
        0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
        50% { opacity: 0.4; }
      }

      /* â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
         10. SCROLL ANIMATIONS
         â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• */

      /* Page fade-in */
      .fade-in {
        animation: fadeInPage 0.7s ease both;
      }
      @keyframes fadeInPage {
        from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
        to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
      }

      /* Section heading slide-in dari kiri */
      .reveal-left {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateX(-32px);
        transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
      }
      .reveal-left.is-visible {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateX(0);
      }

      /* Divider scale-in */
      .reveal-divider {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: scaleX(0.4);
        transform-origin: center;
        transition: opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1);
      }
      .reveal-divider.is-visible {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: scaleX(1);
      }

      /* Card stagger fade-up â€” applied per card oleh JS */
      .reveal-card {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(36px);
        transition:
          opacity 0.55s cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1),
          transform 0.55s cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1);
      }
      .reveal-card.is-visible {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }

      /* Page header text reveal */
      .reveal-up {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
        transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
      }
      .reveal-up.is-visible {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body class="min-h-screen">
    <div id="header-placeholder"></div>

    <main>
      <section class="py-clearance fade-in">
